  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6864286/" class="title-link">这本书是他的精神秘档</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6864286"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/40725476/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/40725476/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">bluesome</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-09-02"
      class="main-meta">2014-09-02 15:31:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6864286_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  那天下着倾盆大雨，一早挤地铁赶到长宁图书馆，去听一场关于《梁漱溟日记》和儒家生活世界的读书会。  读过梁漱溟的《中国文化要义》和《这个世界会好吗》，对他的日记颇有些兴趣。据说，这是一部经历“文革”劫后余生的精神秘档，共80万字，编者撰写了导读性质的前言和每一年...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
